metadata.name: Twitter Banner: NUDE x GM
metadata.description:
"Twitter Banner: NUDE x GM" features an enchanting portrait of a woman, exuding elegance and poise. Encircling the image are the stylized letters "GM" by typography artist @serc1n adding a touch of flair and personalization.

This piece is perfectly sized for a Twitter banner, allowing you to adorn your profile with a statement of support without violating Twitter's community guiedlinesf refined aesthetics.

Size: 15000 x 5000 pixels
